1: commands
2: to move, use arrows
3: to type in insert mode, is I
4: to get back to command mode, is ESC
5: to save -> :w
6: to force-quit -> :q!
7: to write after the cursor -> a
8: new line -> o
9: to delete a line -> dd
10: to delete a character -> del
11: to move to a line -> line number + G
12: replace mode -> R
13: to search -> /yourWord/
14: save and quit -> ZZ
15: to replace text -> sed
